<title>wǒ yǒu yī gè xīn yuàn 迦南1389</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 qīn rén péng yǒu, wǒ yǒu yī gè xīn yuàn, jīn tiān wǒ yào chàng gěi nǐ tīng, qǐng nǐ jì xīn jiān,
 qīn rén péng yǒu, wǒ yǒu yī gè xīn yuàn, jīn tiān wǒ yào chàng gěi nǐ tīng, qǐng nǐ jì xīn jiān,
 zhù yuàn wǒ de zǔ guó hé xié píng ān, zhù yuàn wǒ de qīn rén péng yǒu xìng fú kāng jiàn,
 zhù yuàn wǒ de mín zú yǎng wàng xīng kōng, zhù yuàn wǒ de tóng bāo yǐ ài xiāng lián,
 yǐ ài xiāng lián ài néng huà jiě chóu yuàn, yǐ ài xiāng lián, bù zài yǒu zhàn zhēng xiāo yān,
 yǐ ài xiāng lián sǎ mǎn zǔ guó de hé shān, zhōng huá mín zú yào fù xìng. zhēn ài de gē shēng chuán biàn.
 zhōng huá mín zú yào fù xìng. zhēn ài de gē shēng chuán biàn.</lyrics>
</song>